Developers and Community Members,

The release of Bioconductor 3.7 will be on Tuesday, May 1, 2018. Please see the schedule for details:

  https://www.bioconductor.org/developers/release-schedule/

Over the next month, key deadlines will be announced on the bioc-devel mailing list:

  https://stat.ethz.ch/pipermail/bioc-devel/

Part of preparing for the release is cleaning up the build reports. If you are a package maintainer, please take a look and try to address any problems. Questions about the release or broken packages should be posted to bioc-devel.

  https://www.bioconductor.org/checkResults/

Thanks.

Valerie


