The deadline to submit new packages for inclusion in Bioconductor 3.7 is Monday, April 2.

We cannot guarantee packages submitted by this date will be included in the release as they still need to go through the standard review process. Please note the last day for new packages to be accepted is April 16 which means submissions on April 2 only have a 2 week review window. We'll do our best to move these through quickly.

